----------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components (not bundled; fetched or installed separately)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

- Manim Community Edition — animation engine (MIT License).
  https://www.manim.community/

- Kokoro ONNX neural text-to-speech model weights, fetched by
  pipeline/fetch_models.sh (Apache-2.0; see the kokoro-onnx project).
  https://github.com/thewh1teagle/kokoro-onnx

- FFmpeg — used for the Ken Burns zoompan, particle compositing, and xfade
  stitching (LGPL/GPL depending on build). https://ffmpeg.org/

- A headless Chromium/Chrome is used to rasterize HTML slides to PNG.

