About the example course
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The bundled example (examples/demo-pythagoras/) is an ORIGINAL work created for
this repository on a public-domain mathematical topic. It is provided solely to
demonstrate the pipeline and carries the same Apache-2.0 license as the code.

This pipeline can be pointed at any course material you have the right to use.
Course content you author is yours; do NOT commit copyrighted source textbooks
or course inputs into a repository you publish.
